  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->Reverse<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>functions return the
  <emphasis>source</emphasis> string with all characters in reverse
  order.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting format="linespecific">A := STD.Str.Reverse('ABCDE'); //A contains 'EDCBA'
</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->
